A cyberpunk-style digital fortress under siege: a massive glowing server monolith floats in a neon-lit void, its surface covered in intricate circuit patterns pulsing with electric blue light. Swarms of angular, menacing red data-shards shaped like jagged arrows and broken code fragments assault the structure from multiple angles, trying to pierce through translucent hexagonal shield layers that flicker and ripple on impact. Some red shards have penetrated partially, leaving glowing cracks. A lone hooded figure stands atop the server, wielding a staff that projects defensive barrier waves. The atmosphere is tense, with dramatic purple and cyan lighting, floating holographic diagnostic panels surrounding the scene, and streams of corrupted data visualized as toxic green smoke seeping through vulnerabilities. Rain of binary falls in the background against a dark cityscape of distant server towers.
